msgstr "ደራሲ"

#: climweb/src/climweb/base/templates/admin/plugin_manager.html:111
#, python-format
msgid "Remove plugin %(name)s? This will reverse its database migrations and restart the server."
msgstr "ተሰኪ %(name)s ይወገድ? ይህ የውሂብ ጎታውን ፍልሰት ይለውጣል እና አገልጋዩን እንደገና ያስጀምራል።"

#: climweb/src/climweb/base/templates/admin/plugin_manager.html:113
msgid "Remove"
msgstr "አስወግድ"

#: climweb/src/climweb/base/templates/admin/plugin_manager.html:123
msgid "No plugins are currently installed."
msgstr "በአሁኑ ጊዜ ምንም ተሰኪዎች አልተጫኑም።"

#: climweb/src/climweb/base/templates/admin/plugin_manager.html:127
msgid ""
"Plugins are managed via the <code>CLIMWEB_PLUGIN_GIT_REPOS</code> setting in"
" your <code>.env</code> file. To install, update, or remove a plugin, edit "
"that value and restart the containers."
msgstr ""
"ተሰኪዎች የሚተዳደሩት በ<code>.env</code> ፋይልዎ ውስጥ ባለው "
"የ<code>CLIMWEB_PLUGIN_GIT_REPOS</code> ቅንብር ነው። ተሰኪን ለመጫን፣ ለማዘመን ወይም ለማስወገድ "
"ያንን እሴት ያርትዑ እና መያዣዎቹን እንደገና ያስጀምሩ።"

